{"tid":1077172,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[互動][CLS] 你係山神 山齊士","createTime":"2019-03-25T11:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T16:20:54.000Z","uid":176368,"like":8,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d5e32969c32f3d7c13fc8ae40eb6751b4b5bf030","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"首先多謝呢位巴打，令我又想玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇故等出post太慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[互動故]  我的名字是 沙治奧．拉莫斯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1056430\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1056430</a><br />\n<br />\n故事選項會令其他人觀感以至行為有變化。<br />\n本故事以完季為目標，<br />\n以頭3個回覆為準。<br />\n<br />\n你係山神，今日正式同MK仔互換，<br />\n冬季轉會加盟曼聯，<br />\n你出席曼聯首個記者會，<br />\n打算以鋼琴表演，慶祝神魔合一。<br />\n你會彈咩曲目？<br />\n<br />\nA 阿記會歌<br />\nB 曼聯會歌<br />\nC 歐聯會歌<br />\n<br />\n注意：最正常選項最伏，反之亦然。"},{"pid":"edfb94d6b423a8a7d21bc30b77a51baf1ae6bbe1","tid":1077172,"uid":127164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"a"},{"pid":"3ef3ede20f9bf89c1bb9ac42513321979508441e","tid":1077172,"uid":46608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:02:47.000Z","msg":"d 強國國歌"},{"pid":"dcbf49ba5a0af468d8f2b4934303a5d3fc849931","tid":1077172,"uid":228686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:03:02.000Z","msg":"a"},{"pid":"d9b1afe355cac625b2c0148719f06d1fb4cf6521","tid":1077172,"uid":33533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:03:24.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"09daf72e9a61dd925539a35395c7317cc6368184","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"edfb94d6b423a8a7d21bc30b77a51baf1ae6bbe1","tid":1077172,"uid":127164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"a"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"你係記者會上面完美彈奏出阿記會歌<br />\n當中包含住你既鬥志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n亦有無數委屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n彈完之後見到曼聯高層同摩佬<br />\n成面都係眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來佢地好欣賞你既念舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n摩佬突然走上台，<br />\n講佢其實都好愛車仔，<br />\n你會點答佢：<br />\n<br />\nA 收皮啦廢佬，教好曼9先啦<br />\nB 我深同感受<br />\nC 你返去教車仔，我做住領隊先"},{"pid":"513b5bd3ae4bd0fde80faf1887b406ddc49a56ef","tid":1077172,"uid":127164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09daf72e9a61dd925539a35395c7317cc6368184","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"edfb94d6b423a8a7d21bc30b77a51baf1ae6bbe1","tid":1077172,"uid":127164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"a"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"你係記者會上面完美彈奏出阿記會歌<br />\n當中包含住你既鬥志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n亦有無數委屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n彈完之後見到曼聯高層同摩佬<br />\n成面都係眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來佢地好欣賞你既念舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n摩佬突然走上台，<br />\n講佢其實都好愛車仔，<br />\n你會點答佢：<br />\n<br />\nA 收皮啦廢佬，教好曼9先啦<br />\nB 我深同感受<br />\nC 你返去教車仔，我做住領隊先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"c"},{"pid":"8aeca1a6e2821f6e8894a9e37b70a0ec75d90b21","tid":1077172,"uid":228686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:25:48.000Z","msg":"c"},{"pid":"17df0ffb45193a5ec4d82d4d9addbc945fe4216c","tid":1077172,"uid":199804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:32:02.000Z","msg":"C , Gchi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1cbd354030e89b9ccaebcfea2fd12759eeff6f","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17df0ffb45193a5ec4d82d4d9addbc945fe4216c","tid":1077172,"uid":199804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:32:02.000Z","msg":"C , Gchi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T13:21:22.000Z","msg":"於是，摩佬第二日就辭咗職，<br />\n因為你冇教練牌，<br />\n球會搵咗蘇斯克查幫你。<br />\n你第一次以曼聯球員同領隊身份出戰，<br />\n會係英格蘭足總盃作客對英乙伊奧維，<br />\n你會搵邊兩個球員同你配合？<br />\n（開放式問題：<br />\n你打左翼，第一個名前鋒，第二個名攻中）<br />\n<br />\n頭2個選項邊個like最快到3"},{"pid":"29f6b20aab981a68352bf232dbdc4d99fa414274","tid":1077172,"uid":58375,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T13:33:37.000Z","msg":"前鋒蘇斯克查<br />\n攻中卡域克"},{"pid":"050f10260976530d8388861438ff757903b82347","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T13:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gaHWjGn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgaHWjGn.jpg&h=b176d3bd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n領隊出席記者會"},{"pid":"1f0d54c1bd5af3f90bede202bdb5f26c2ae5d4e8","tid":1077172,"uid":228686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"歐偉倫<br />\n李健和"},{"pid":"86262e182c0e8e7590871835a56d834c81802a99","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"29f6b20aab981a68352bf232dbdc4d99fa414274","tid":1077172,"uid":58375,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T13:33:37.000Z","msg":"前鋒蘇斯克查<br />\n攻中卡域克"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T14:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S9AEhEn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS9AEhEn.jpg&h=11b5432e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83fa3628a01c5a98bc3c204fbc51186eacdbd952","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"你用 對勝利充滿渴望嘅眼神 步入球場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n前鋒 係你嘅助教蘇斯克查，<br />\n攻中 係你教練團隊入面嘅 卡域克。<br />\n開波之前 蘇斯克查同你講：<br />\n「 教練多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我有好多年冇試過正選上陣。」<br />\n「一陣你幫我拉開對手。」<br />\n<br />\n卡域克同你講：「 其實我唔係好識打攻中。」<br />\n「 放心！一陣聽我指揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」<br />\n<br />\n開波幾分鐘， 有個Mark你既後衛恥笑你：<br />\n「咁大間球會連球員都唔夠？」<br />\n<br />\n你面對挑釁，決定用行動證明自己，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你示意卡域克傳波俾你喺禁區頂偏左，<br />\n你打算：<br />\n<br />\nA 傳波俾入攝嘅蘇斯克查（成功率高）<br />\nB 一夜省落啱啱笑你嘅後衛（成功率低）<br />\nC 對著遠處燙死角（成功率一般）"},{"pid":"034534ba60c1aa3b33f03c6064d162e8312bdfb8","tid":1077172,"uid":228686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T14:59:53.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"dcdf5f17360826307578e1530d907343871f59fc","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:07:13.000Z","msg":"c"},{"pid":"e5748f82377495633a951fd9acd966567ebca4a1","tid":1077172,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:08:47.000Z","msg":"c"},{"pid":"0654e6d977d26ddf1224a97121b80263619c2523","tid":1077172,"uid":227331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T17:33:29.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"ea0c9661739fe2a39f8f32a0fe310fc53d2e73b8","tid":1077172,"uid":112031,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T19:15:42.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"911d5900d0b42903fef35a34fbe1428f3e742e4e","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e5748f82377495633a951fd9acd966567ebca4a1","tid":1077172,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T15:08:47.000Z","msg":"c"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:03:23.000Z","msg":"（頭3個選項有2個C）<br />\n為咗先開記錄，你決定自己把握機會，<br />\n下次先教訓恥笑你球會既對手，<br />\n何況你冇信心一定省中。<br />\n娃娃臉既走位幫你拉開一對中堅，<br />\n你趁機瞄準龍門右上角，施展看家本領，<br />\n球波係一對中堅之間穿過，<br />\n守門員起跳！<br />\n竟然手指尖輕微接觸到個波！<br />\n個波睇落好似要撞住！<br />\n呢個時候你大叫：<br />\n<br />\nA 上啊密林號！（試圖加速個波）<br />\nB 上啊青龍白虎朱雀玄武！（試圖增加旋轉）<br />\nC 縮細電筒！（試圖縮細個波）"},{"pid":"840f06dd7696d161e7da3cc195a8750072347319","tid":1077172,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:07:23.000Z","msg":"c"},{"pid":"5d38af750cefb2bc3513fc25caee6561ca653694","tid":1077172,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"c"},{"pid":"237341ff5d404a1345e17714b4c7dbbea23ee66c","tid":1077172,"uid":228686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:53:43.000Z","msg":"b"},{"pid":"021af1d887efda4e12ff0062575cb9ed45b96afa","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"840f06dd7696d161e7da3cc195a8750072347319","tid":1077172,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:07:23.000Z","msg":"c"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:57:27.000Z","msg":"你估唔到自己竟然有超能力，<br />\n你大叫：「縮細電筒！」<br />\n個波即刻縮細到得返一個網球咁，<br />\n本來會撞柱彈出，但竟然撞内柱彈入！<br />\n你即刻將個波變返原本大細，<br />\n個個人都以爲自己眼花，<br />\n好驚嘆你既超精准射門，<br />\n唯獨係場邊有一個人令你有D不安&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n因爲你排既進攻組合非常唔夾，<br />\n卡域克唔識做攻中，蘇斯克查又冇態，<br />\n1:0 比數維持到 80分鐘，<br />\n突然，你有最後一個黃金機會，<br />\n你位於左路禁區K角位插入，<br />\n前面竟然係 之前挑癮你 既中堅！<br />\n你決定：<br />\n<br />\nA 冇理個波，雙腳飛剷佢<br />\nB 接應傳球，一野轟落去下體<br />\nC 接應傳球，一野爆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（之後會繼續劇情）"},{"pid":"fcb3940a5af64d89ad18e887e27f25dd6cdbbc73","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T08:25:28.000Z","msg":"b"},{"pid":"7d118b74e4cd0fcf6cb51b87dbde32de81a86635","tid":1077172,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T08:49:10.000Z","msg":"b"},{"pid":"714da9470a97a5a07b215edacb1eaf5cffaa65ff","tid":1077172,"uid":228686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"021af1d887efda4e12ff0062575cb9ed45b96afa","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"840f06dd7696d161e7da3cc195a8750072347319","tid":1077172,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:07:23.000Z","msg":"c"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:57:27.000Z","msg":"你估唔到自己竟然有超能力，<br />\n你大叫：「縮細電筒！」<br />\n個波即刻縮細到得返一個網球咁，<br />\n本來會撞柱彈出，但竟然撞内柱彈入！<br />\n你即刻將個波變返原本大細，<br />\n個個人都以爲自己眼花，<br />\n好驚嘆你既超精准射門，<br />\n唯獨係場邊有一個人令你有D不安&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n因爲你排既進攻組合非常唔夾，<br />\n卡域克唔識做攻中，蘇斯克查又冇態，<br />\n1:0 比數維持到 80分鐘，<br />\n突然，你有最後一個黃金機會，<br />\n你位於左路禁區K角位插入，<br />\n前面竟然係 之前挑癮你 既中堅！<br />\n你決定：<br />\n<br />\nA 冇理個波，雙腳飛剷佢<br />\nB 接應傳球，一野轟落去下體<br />\nC 接應傳球，一野爆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（之後會繼續劇情）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T10:37:12.000Z","msg":"b"},{"pid":"d550898ba021a5129081fd31f6beaf064c0ce601","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fcb3940a5af64d89ad18e887e27f25dd6cdbbc73","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T08:25:28.000Z","msg":"b"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:24:41.000Z","msg":"你由邊路插入禁區，<br />\n接應卡域克俾你既致命直線，<br />\n前面有個後衛封阻射門角度，<br />\n此人之前恥笑你隊波唔夠人用！<br />\n你一於對住佢下體 抽個波埋去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「啊～姨～哦～」<br />\n佢下體同波產生激烈摩擦，<br />\n身體不由自主咁扭動，<br />\n竟然開始呻吟起上黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n褲襠好似有紅白色液體流出！？<br />\n估唔到你山神既球技令到男人高潮！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你頂唔順差D作嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n決定逃離現場！（1：0完場）<br />\n係球員通道見到同你交換去阿記既 MK仔，<br />\n佢細細聲同你講：<br />\n「你要小心一個人，就係佢陷害我！<br />\n你要先下手為強！」<br />\n<br />\n此人係？<br />\n（必須係知名曼聯球員）"},{"pid":"5085422723fbfba8e4ba5a2a90299c6a6d1a84b4","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:26:01.000Z","msg":"迪基亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd6d094fecac9d38e1df392a1b832769510db28","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:33:43.000Z","msg":"（會用最快達到3個like既回覆）"},{"pid":"32fc82b50e6ecded7a2acb0bd2f8491e7c060366","tid":1077172,"uid":92002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:39:24.000Z","msg":"C朗"},{"pid":"9104cd780300dd337adaf22a2eff810ce4406a56","tid":1077172,"uid":185435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"De gea"},{"pid":"2fa879253be08dffaa384ed0294b16be723f7b96","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5085422723fbfba8e4ba5a2a90299c6a6d1a84b4","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:26:01.000Z","msg":"迪基亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:02:11.000Z","msg":"（ 接受你嘅挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\nMk仔同你講陷害佢嘅知名曼聯球員<br />\n就係球隊最緊要嘅人物：迪迪仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終佢喺軍中受到球員擁戴，<br />\n你唔係好相信 mk仔嘅說話，<br />\n但決定喺嚟緊對熱刺嘅英超處子戰<br />\n試探一下佢。<br />\n<br />\n係賽前部署嘅時候，<br />\n你特登邀請所有一隊球員參與，<br />\n趁機會叫迪迪仔建議一下排陣，<br />\n佢笑住講：「連美斯應該同你一齊打攻中，<br />\n前面就出福仔一個啦。」<br />\n<br />\n其實前一晚你check過迪基亞嘅瀏覽紀錄，<br />\n發現佢有聽開某小區講波佬 何蛇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係話迪迪仔知道 正三角形組合<br />\n既不能主攻破密集（冇拉邊），<br />\n又冇最好既反擊力（2個超連結人）。<br />\n不過你冇 揭發佢嘅陰毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n你仲建議：「 你腳法咁好，又高大，<br />\n一於同我打前鋒啦！亅<br />\n<br />\n（下場對熱刺，請揀兩個對手出場）"},{"pid":"b74b899dd6f2f714cc4aea6799415f7160d3bcf7","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:09:56.000Z","msg":"拳王阿里<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 丹尼路斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c2fb90a34f90d399c8cb6255dfd76483d2f308","tid":1077172,"uid":209193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:11:33.000Z","msg":"拉美拿 dele 撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb10fa249e4a5e49c9eca2cba2c08ac91a96119","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T16:25:03.000Z","msg":"回揀上面like較多既選項"},{"pid":"e1f25ccddd426381c6012db8eb81442c9d58463b","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b74b899dd6f2f714cc4aea6799415f7160d3bcf7","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:09:56.000Z","msg":"拳王阿里<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 丹尼路斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T02:31:13.000Z","msg":"今日係同熱刺決戰既大日子，<br />\n你係球員通道上等緊出場，<br />\n突然你見到隔離走埋黎一個高大又留鬚既男人，<br />\n原來佢係皇馬同西班牙國家隊長！<br />\n沙治奧拉莫斯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拉狗笑笑口講：「我特登黎觀察你，下場挑你機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！」<br />\n你覺得好奇怪，明明黎緊歐聯打西維爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n拉狗：「你有冇搞錯？！我一早轉會利記啦屌你，<br />\n我仲同謝老四 廢托 好夾添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n原來你既抉擇唔止有蝴蝶效應，仲引起時空交錯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比賽開始！<br />\n你知道丹尼路斯剛剛抑鬱病好返，<br />\n打算出其不意，令到佢精神不穩，<br />\n你控住個波，決定&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n（開放式答案，會揀頭3個選項其中最多 like）"},{"pid":"55c18ebd9c745d83f8b16ff96596a84afbc22dc9","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T02:37:25.000Z","msg":"收山腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ad604ce3cf23c7611750f51004a429409bc632","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T02:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傳個波比rose 再黎一下收山腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1f012d874e8c647712419914f11296dee1316b2d","tid":1077172,"uid":198402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T02:56:08.000Z","msg":"中埸遠射直入龍"},{"pid":"30eaedebd39f7f021d38ca875cb028e5dea93fa1","tid":1077172,"uid":136116,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T03:23:37.000Z","msg":"好似簡迪咁 收山腳飛鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e14eebccf094fbe268110ce1f9ce52fc4e3adb","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30eaedebd39f7f021d38ca875cb028e5dea93fa1","tid":1077172,"uid":136116,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T03:23:37.000Z","msg":"好似簡迪咁 收山腳飛鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:18:57.000Z","msg":"你帶住個波向 玫瑰  衝去，<br />\n佢打算 mark住你 有空檔 先偷你個波，<br />\n但你竟然主動 將個波面對面交畀佢，<br />\n佢一時之間 反應唔切，<br />\n你就好似毒男簡迪 一野飛鏟埋佢，<br />\n你右腳中波，左腳連消帶打！<br />\n「啊！～屌我媽好痛～亅<br />\n<br />\n玫瑰突然之間抑鬱復發！<br />\n佢好痛恨自己點解咁廢，<br />\n點解阿媽要改自己名做 玫瑰，<br />\n打算自己閉氣 了結自己生命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你恥笑佢：「睇開D啦！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為你知道叫抑鬱病人樂觀D係一種侮辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玫瑰俾你激到氣絕，一命嗚呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候 拳王阿里 飛埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你 電光火石之間眼前一閃，<br />\n原來已經中咗 日字衝拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n其實你跟葉問學過功夫，<br />\n阿里爸爸就係你師叔，<br />\n你會點樣對付師弟阿里？<br />\n<br />\nA 施丹頭鎚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB 穿心腿！<br />\nC 認真打一場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2d2c9e8f63e0f0eaf0d3f65350747cc7bf8bd4","tid":1077172,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:23:28.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"30703d2f19d60c706ac67d566ca8ed159dbc306c","tid":1077172,"uid":107249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T15:36:02.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"a8abe34401149b7215d235daa072556204b204b2","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:19:42.000Z","msg":"c MMA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d6e43e8738f0b37b2042a4f7b2062206b3dba2","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8abe34401149b7215d235daa072556204b204b2","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:19:42.000Z","msg":"c MMA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"一場同門師兄弟對決即將要開始！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係 斷J流大師兄<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阿里係 外賣condom仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1W08ay.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1W08ay.png&h=1a67da8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年你兩個比試過無數次，<br />\n但都係點到即止，留力不留手，<br />\n今次終於可以大展拳腳，以解心頭之憤！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n球證顛恩突然閃出，隔係你地之間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n唔通想阻止你地打鬥？<br />\n顛恩一表嚴肅：「請移玉步至中圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n按照江湖規矩，身體任何部位觸碰圈外地下算輸，<br />\n10秒昏迷不醒算技術性擊倒，<br />\n輸既一方球隊會被罰 3:0 ！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n決鬥開始！你地兩個都好謹慎，<br />\n唔敢輕易進攻以免露出破綻，<br />\n你突然靈光一閃，<br />\n記得阿記學院 武學教授雲爺爺 傳授過你一招生平絕學，<br />\n可以一擊秒殺，唔死都重傷！<br />\n你使出&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n（開放性問題，越cls越好）"},{"pid":"8e8880b14db6b6157c2943fcf5b53fe1189ec8b8","tid":1077172,"uid":204373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"星爆氣流斬"},{"pid":"6b007aef559ae2affc4807bbeec135f9e2d9c738","tid":1077172,"uid":185435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T07:44:42.000Z","msg":"降龍十八掌"},{"pid":"dbc7f079ce41ce78233556d8009a027732e4b1cf","tid":1077172,"uid":1187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:11:04.000Z","msg":"...jm9"},{"pid":"44a54033ea2ddc78d5e889f2bd6cdd6a3ff32612","tid":1077172,"uid":59575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"4d3841ade1e3bd0d01c61af18fd02dadba8d86eb","tid":1077172,"uid":225798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:54:18.000Z","msg":"樓主夠創意 正評左"},{"pid":"a5ef1683722ac664f14c6de469f9cd656ac9327b","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44a54033ea2ddc78d5e889f2bd6cdd6a3ff32612","tid":1077172,"uid":59575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"B"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:20:56.000Z","msg":"今次冇選項<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9dee09233106969989452980ccb7530e52b4ee","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T09:28:51.000Z","msg":"龜波氣功"},{"pid":"2dd571820f5ad732e1e9d2480b04aad4d93dcd1b","tid":1077172,"uid":228686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T10:24:51.000Z","msg":"萬佛朝宗"},{"pid":"d213fa8d8567fcce95a1c18f7920b3bbbb445ad6","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T11:22:46.000Z","msg":"癲恩係熱狗 會唔會加入戰鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1805544c2c845a76cf455b0cbd61d374a6a91d","tid":1077172,"uid":134546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:28:34.000Z","msg":"大聲叫出技能名<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><em>清熱酷</em></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"410d71a03220ebb7d137a772db2b47315db8ac2c","tid":1077172,"uid":17817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:35:29.000Z","msg":"奪命較剪腳"},{"pid":"a18b5fc6010ddd44e0f465ecf1c9f67101d03006","tid":1077172,"uid":149607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:41:37.000Z","msg":"G chi"},{"pid":"0634ed8caa7d3e5760bb83236feb75a378e6b917","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b1805544c2c845a76cf455b0cbd61d374a6a91d","tid":1077172,"uid":134546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:28:34.000Z","msg":"大聲叫出技能名<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><em>清熱酷</em></strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:22:41.000Z","msg":"你同拳王阿里互相對峙於球場中圈內，<br />\n四周觀眾吶喊助威，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本來你兩個係同門師兄弟，<br />\n但你自從拜雲爺爺為師，實力厚實不少！<br />\n你打算速戰速決，使出必殺技，<br />\n「清清清 熱熱熱 酷酷酷！！！」<br />\n此乃實而不華 亦暗藏乾坤的招式，<br />\n源自清除體內劇毒、起死回生之術！<br />\n經武學教授同你既鑽研後，<br />\n將 清熱酷 威力放大1百萬倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n中招者陰盛陽衰而死！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係0.1秒之內：你右手舉高向天 左手向地，<br />\n畫一個大圈，之後雙手拎住一支清熱酷，<br />\n同時召喚出12支清熱酷分佈係唔同方位！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拳王阿里大吃一驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n但都係你萬劍齊發既一瞬間，<br />\n使出 普捷天師 教既插水大法！<br />\n將命中既部位減到最低......<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（下回繼續！）"},{"pid":"b7bd51930adaa4c67ca40a9fa66bd9d06e2b2abf","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:38:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a6c21c2bfc1df366402961f4eb4e7d0abe7e5bf","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7bd51930adaa4c67ca40a9fa66bd9d06e2b2abf","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:38:00.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3944ab4f550e2e5e3f9a00bfd896fabfd7319ece","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"球場上落完一陣「清熱酷雨」，<br />\n霧氣逐漸散去，<br />\n中圈内只有你仍然屹立！<br />\n拳王阿里訓咗係出面，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然一息尚存，但已經冇力再企起身，<br />\n身為熱狗嘅癲恩無可奈何判你勝出，<br />\n最聯以 3:0 擊敗熱狗！<br />\n（平行時空 熱 2:0 曼）<br />\n<br />\n熱刺元氣大傷，今季已經威脅唔到你，<br />\n但下一場就係雙紅會！<br />\n面對 沙治奧拉莫斯 帶領嘅利記，<br />\n仲有死神藍斯既加盟 究竟會點發展？<br />\n<br />\n經過剛剛一場，球隊士氣大振，<br />\n已經封你做 奧脫福之鬼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n神魔合一！魔性澎湃！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你諗起25仔 敵機啊（迪迪仔），<br />\n已經不足爲患，可以將佢貶爲後備，<br />\n依家你要決定龍門人選。<br />\n<br />\n（開放性答案，下場將會穩守反擊）"},{"pid":"8a63088aa7d6748451299f5b93ab43e685529639","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:14:16.000Z","msg":"摩連奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500cb841e7e1d99a4df302f11615be91d8734079","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8a63088aa7d6748451299f5b93ab43e685529639","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:14:16.000Z","msg":"摩連奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T07:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CpnHgON.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCpnHgON.jpg&h=717d5eca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f8a73072cbd3de812412a654d34cf567320dfd9","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T18:29:47.000Z","msg":"推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2843c6dc1f86b2288850ca204e01b1205c8778","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f8a73072cbd3de812412a654d34cf567320dfd9","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T18:29:47.000Z","msg":"推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T12:09:45.000Z","msg":"最近太忙，短時間內補返篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc982876ebfe2361c49c7718ad2760148ff5e45","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:06:39.000Z","msg":"雙紅會係一場非常關鍵既比賽，<br />\n因為 25仔 敵機啊 已經畀你貶為後備，<br />\n所以你考慮緊列 羅尾露 做正選門將，<br />\n呢個時候有個神秘電話打黎，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「嗚嗚嗚咽... ...有家歸不得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n原來係 摩佬，乾地 教緊車仔嘛，<br />\n邊會有人睬佢呢，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDaddy：「有冇工好介紹啊？」<br />\n你諗住恥笑佢：「打龍就有你份！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「我都打過友誼賽既龍，一於咁話啦！」<br />\n你：「<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />... ...」<br />\n<br />\n比賽當日，你排出4312，<br />\n呢個係極穩固既防反陣式，<br />\n讓出控球權令利記冇機會打反擊！<br />\n針對佢地老鼠拉龜既控球在腳！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你做超連結人，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前面係速度型球員 福仔 馬仔，<br />\n預計用反擊入到2球波，<br />\n關鍵在於防線發揮，<br />\n一對中堅你會用... ...<br />\n<br />\n（開放性問題，必須為曼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"496c112bc7f7a9acce4d6e6ce4a653e990ee1d00","tid":1077172,"uid":134546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T17:30:04.000Z","msg":"Carrick McTom"},{"pid":"8303fc89872879eadd1c1f0b26e8c22fbbf994cd","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T05:07:27.000Z","msg":"lukaku"},{"pid":"4ec93208e7c9f04abf2764be2711920c03bcf978","tid":1077172,"uid":6898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T06:07:55.000Z","msg":"sob 老廢"},{"pid":"2a70a57ffe52689092d9ac6269fb83fba47aa928","tid":1077172,"uid":204373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T14:36:09.000Z","msg":"左羊右華"},{"pid":"53f2c6213c379748eb461c246c181cfd83a0dfca","tid":1077172,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T08:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157d2205cfcae880cc37873f3aeaaaf78811ba18","tid":1077172,"uid":125070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:34:34.000Z","msg":"盧卡古 sob"},{"pid":"3121d95745111ef6f6873622670bf2d72b74ae8f","tid":1077172,"uid":176368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:34:30.000Z","msg":"對付利記咁高級數既對手，<br />\n當然要搵返有輝煌戰績既球員，<br />\n你揀既其中一人係空中霸王，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多次將黃金機會瓦解，<br />\n無數個必入波都化為灰燼！<br />\n佢就係攻勢終結者&mdash;&mdash;渣古！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一個人選就係你既得力助手So B，<br />\n上次同你係前面衝鋒陷陣，<br />\n今次由佢領導防線，<br />\n仲有機會使出必殺技&mdash;&mdash;娃娃臉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比賽正式開始！<br />\n你趁 摩懶奴 同 懦夫暈 係草地上訓緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n示意馬仔 福仔衝入禁區，<br />\n你吊個高波俾佢地，眼見就落到禁區... ...<br />\n<br />\n突然 馬福仔 雙雙跣低！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只見世界第一中堅 雲迪克 使出一招草木皆兵！<br />\n將佢地腳下既草地轉移，<br />\n因為釘鞋一時抓唔住，令人失去平衡！<br />\n<br />\n你意識到，呢場波同網球王子一樣，<br />\n冇超能力根本唔使旨意玩！"}]}